<html>
	<head>
		<meta charset='utf-8' />
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: #333;
				max-width: 600px;
				margin: 0 auto;
			}
			.header {
				background-color: #4f46e5;
				color: white;
				padding: 20px;
				text-align: center;
				border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
			}
			.content {
				padding: 20px;
				border: 1px solid #ddd;
				border-top: none;
				border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
			}
			.ticket-details {
				background-color: #f9f9f9;
				border: 1px solid #eee;
				border-radius: 5px;
				padding: 15px;
				margin: 20px 0;
			}
			.qr-code {
				text-align: center;
				margin: 30px 0;
			}
			.footer {
				text-align: center;
				font-size: 12px;
				color: #666;
				margin-top: 30px;
			}
			.button {
				display: inline-block;
				background-color: #4f46e5;
				color: white;
				text-decoration: none;
				padding: 10px 20px;
				border-radius: 5px;
				margin-top: 20px;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class='header'>
			<h1>Your Ticket is Ready!</h1>
		</div>

		<div class='content'>
			<p>Hello {{name}},</p>

			<p>Thank you for purchasing a ticket to
				<strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>. Your ticket has been confirmed and is
				ready to use.</p>

			<div class='ticket-details'>
				<h3>Ticket Details:</h3>
				<p><strong>Event:</strong> {{eventTitle}}</p>
				<p><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{eventDate}}</p>
				<p><strong>Location:</strong> {{eventLocation}}</p>
				<p><strong>Ticket ID:</strong> {{ticketId}}</p>
				<p><strong>Price:</strong> ${{price}}</p>
			</div>

			{{#if hasPDF}}
				<p>
					<strong>We've attached your PDF ticket to this email.</strong>
					You can print it or just show it on your mobile device at the
					entrance.
				</p>
			{{/if}}

			<div class='qr-code'>
				<p><strong>Show this QR code at the event entrance:</strong></p>
				<img
					src='{{qrCode}}'
					alt='Ticket QR Code'
					style='max-width: 200px; height: auto;'
				/>
			</div>

			<p>You can also access all your tickets in your profile on our platform:</p>

			<div style='text-align: center;'>
				<a href='{{ticketUrl}}' class='button'>View My Tickets</a>
			</div>

			<p>We're looking forward to seeing you at the event!</p>

			<p>Best regards,<br />UEvent Team</p>
		</div>

		<div class='footer'>
			<p>This is an automated message, please do not reply to this email.</p>
			<p>UEvent &copy; 2023. All rights reserved.</p>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>